        i0.ɵɵelementStart(223, "mat-card-content");
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(224, "p", 16);
        i0.ɵɵtext(225, " David Howard Thornton is an American actor originally from Huntsville, AL. Now based in New York City, he continues his stage, film, and voice over work. He is best known for his roles as \"Grandpa Who\" in the 1st to 5th national tours of \"Dr. Seuss' How the Grinch Stole Christmas: The Musical\", the voice of \"Shizoku\" and others in the video game \"Invizimals: The Lost Kingdom.\" David has also portrayed \"The Joker\" in the YouTube series, \"Nightwing Escalation.\" Most notably and to critical acclaim, David portrays \"Art the Clown\" in the horror film \"Terrifier\" and will reprise his role as \"Art\" in the upcoming sequel, \"Terrifier 2.\" David will also be seen in the upcoming films \"The Dark Offerings\" and \"Stream.\" ");
