        i0.ɵɵelementStart(235, "mat-card-content");
        i0.ɵɵelementStart(236, "p", 16);
        i0.ɵɵtext(237, " Denver - \u201CColorado Festival of Horror (COFOH) 2022: Funhouse\u201D returns for our second year September 9, 10, and 11, 2022, at the Embassy Suites by Hilton Denver Central Park, 4444 N. Havana St, Denver, CO 80239. COFOH is an intimate fan experience and convention for all things horror, featuring celebrity guests, artists, writers, vendors, panels and so much more. In that screaming tradition COFOH is proud to announce actress, producer and director Lynn Lowry of THE CRAZIES and SHIVERS fame! ");
        i0.ɵɵelement(238, "br");
        i0.ɵɵelement(239, "br");
        i0.ɵɵtext(240, " Lynn Lowry is an American born actress who\u2019s been performing, directing and producing for five decades. She is best known for the cult classic horror films, I DRINK YOUR BLOOD, THE CRAZIES, SHIVERS and CAT PEOPLE. But her professional career really began when at seventeen she acted opposite the sixteen-year-old John Belushi at the Shawnee Summer Theatre in Bloomfield, Indiana. Shortly after that Lynn went to New York where she starred opposite Peter Fonda in FIGHTING MAD directed by academy award winner, Jonathan Demme. She was a regular on the soap opera, HOW TO SURVIVE A MARRIAGE opposite F. Murray Abraham and Brad Davis and also acted in ANOTHER WORLD. ");
        i0.ɵɵelement(241, "br");
        i0.ɵɵelement(242, "br");
        i0.ɵɵtext(243, " While in New York, Lynn studied all styles of theatre, becoming a producer and director at the Off-Broadway Theatre, The Production Company and did three plays at the famed Manhattan Theatre Club. In the past 20 years, Lynn has been singing with her jazz trio in Los Angeles and doing a multitude of Indy Films. She\u2019s won thirteen Best Actress Awards for her work in MODEL HUNGER, BASEMENT JACK, THE PERIPHERAL and READY FOR MY CLOSE-UP and three Lifetime Achievement Awards at various film festivals. ");
        i0.ɵɵelement(244, "br");
        i0.ɵɵelement(245, "br");
        i0.ɵɵtext(246, " Lynn Lowry was very fortunate to have had the opportunity to work with George A. Romero, David Cronenberg, David E. Durston, Paul Schrader and many more wonderful directors. They provided her with a priceless legacy that will never die. ");
        i0.ɵɵelement(247, "br");
        i0.ɵɵelement(248, "br");
        i0.ɵɵtext(249, " COFOH: Colorado Festival of Horror is preparing for its second-year event highlighting the horror genre, and all that it bleeds. ");
        i0.ɵɵelement(250, "br");
        i0.ɵɵelement(251, "br");
        i0.ɵɵtext(252, " COFOH will be a platform for the community to unite over the love of horror and everything that creeps in the night! For more information and event tickets visit us on our ");
